{{Infobox Athleticrace | bgcolour = #FE9A2E | image = File:Stade Léopold Sédar Senghor.jpg | imagesize = 180px | caption = Stade Léopold Sédar Senghor | date = May | location = [[Dakar]], [[Senegal]] | type = [[Track and field]] | est = 2003 | homepage = [http://www.meeting-dakar.com/ meeting-dakar.com] }}
The '''Meeting Grand Prix IAAF de Dakar''' is a [[track and field]] competition at the [[Léopold Sédar Senghor]] [[Stade Leopold Senghor|Stadium]] in [[Dakar]], [[Senegal]] as part of the [[IAAF World Challenge Meetings]]. It was first organized in 2003 as Meeting International d'Athletisme de la Ville de Dakar. From 2006 to 2009 the [[International Association of Athletics Federations|IAAF]] classified the Meeting Grand Prix IAAF de Dakar among [[IAAF Grand Prix]] meetings. From the 2008 edition on it has its current name.
